scene.message:
Nanjo: I agree with his view.{nl}
A man like Kandori could{nl}
make biological weapons{nl}
without batting an eye.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Why's everyone so{nl}
hung up on SEBEC? It's just{nl}
a company.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I didn't know you{nl}
liked gossip so much. Now{nl}
wrap it up, we're going{nl}
to the hospital.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: SEBEC being cursed{nl}
is just a kids' rumor! What{nl}
they're really making is{nl}
biological weapons, for sure.{waitkey}{ret}
